summary: This is an FBI FD-302 form documenting a proffer interview conducted on September 10, 2019, at the Southern District of New York. The interview was attended by two Assistant United States Attorneys, an FBI Special Agent, and an Office of the Inspector General representative. The document is a summary of information provided by an individual under a proffer agreement.
